Isatou Jallow (amụrụ n'October 10, 1997) bụ onye Gambia na-agba bọọlụ, onye na-agba maka ndị otu mba Gambia
Ọ nọchitere anya Gambia n'oge gara aga n'oge na-erubeghị afọ, tupu ọ gaa n'òtù ndị isi mba
Na klọb, ọ na-egwuri egwu maka Rivers Angels na Nigeria Women Premier League Tupu ọ banye Angels, ọ na-egwuri egwu maka F.C
